text: I just found this network throttle utility, provided by apple in a "Hardware IO Tools for XCode" bundle
inlcudes such profiles as "Very Bad Network", "High Latency DNS", and "100% Loss"
The icon is giving me a headache
I want to rename the "Very Bad Network" profile to "Uncorked Studios Central"
There's also a  "HomeKit Accessory Simulator" in the bundle - could be interesting.

attachments.title: If programming languages were weapons • Bjorn Tipling
attachments.text: C is an M1 Garand standard issue rifle, old but reliable. C++ is a set of nunchuks, powerful and impressive when wielded but takes many years of pain to master and often you probably wish you were using something else. Perl is a molotov cocktail,... | Bjorn Tipling | Software Engineer at @floobits
